text: Clarice Hanson (23 March 1911 - 23 December 1956) was a British gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1911 births Category:1956 deaths Category:British female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Great Britain Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bradford
